title: My Eyes - Good Omens Animatic
author: Double S
comment: The rainbow in Aziraphale's eyes made him realize he is gay-

I have never seen someone do an animatic with Noah’s Ark start and the highlights of humanity’s flaws and celebrations after their downfalls. AWH THE RAINBOW ARC. 
This animatic is seriously rad! AND THE SWITCHING OF PERSPECTIVES IS GOOD 
I REALLY FELT THIS

No one:

Me: *tries to sing both parts at the same time*
Crowley and Aziraphale interacting with humanity is my favorite type of animatic, I love they’re different perspectives (Aziraphale’s bits are so beautiful and wholesome)
Wow. A duet where you can actually understand the overlapping lyrics! Also nice animation. :)
